des:
Hear seven different barnyard animal alarms and 3 special snooze sounds in this realistic collection of classic farm animal sounds.
Roosters, chickens, horses, cows, sheep, geese, pigs, and more! 
Wake up every day like you're living on the farm! 

FEEDBACK AND SUPPORT:
If you enjoyed Barnyard Animals Alarm, please leave us a review telling us what you love, and what alarms you want to hear next!

LEARN MORE:
Created by Volley - the makers of the hit Alexa games Song Quiz, Yes Sire, Popcorn Tycoon, and Bedtime Stories.
